      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JAW DROPPER (4) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Maiden winner three back (17.88) at this track over 324m. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Key player on best and worth another chance. DYNA TWIST (1) has found the minor placings here at last couple of runs, finishing second last time beaten 4.5 lengths (17.90). Has a win and eight places times at this track. Likely to be in the finish again. BAD GIRL BERRY (7) was an effortless winner two back scoring by 2.5 lengths then well held latest finishing a 10 length 8th at this track (18.42). Solid formlines coming through her last run. Bold showing expected. REDEMPTIONIST (2) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can bounce back.",
